Cable Replacement BGProject Code For BlueGiga BLE112 Module

This is based on Bluetooth Smart Cable Replacement App Note from BlueGiga

USE:
- Install Bluegiga BLE SW Update Tool
- Attach CC Debugger to BLE Module
- Open project.bgproj to start update tool
- Press 'Update' button on lower right to upload firmware

NOTES:
- UART Channel 0, Alt 1 is being used for RX/TX. Flow control is off. Other USART 
	channels can be used by changing settings in hardware.xml. See BLE112 Datasheet
	for pin assignment details.